{"name":"Nerve Jammer","type":"pharmaceutical","img":"systems/vastgrimm/assets/images/icons/pharmaceuticals/syringe.png","data":{"description":"<p>Injectable, Nerve Jammers cause the user to &ldquo;feel no pain in the membrane.&rdquo; All damage is recorded as 1&frasl;2 damage for up to 4 rounds. After 4 rounds, the user needs twice the amount of usual rest to recover the HP. Addiction: 1-5 (d20).</p>","equipped":false,"price":0,"quantity":1,"volume":0.05,"weight":0.05,"addiction":5},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"2oqn6Iy7EPH48MYr":3},"flags":{},"_id":"5cEhUPYknbxVqGtn"}
{"name":"Yellow Jacket","type":"pharmaceutical","img":"systems/vastgrimm/assets/images/icons/pharmaceuticals/capsule.png","data":{"description":"<p>Yellow Jackets are large yellow and black pills (usually) that act as superpowerful antihistamines. A typical waterproof sleeve holds 1-20 pills. All Toughness tests vs Poison, Infection, Infestation (including w&uuml;rms) etc. are reduced by 2 for 1 day per pill. Pills/Bonuses cannot be stacked. Yellow Jackets are non-addictive and highly sought after and often attract those who would rather take than bargain. Addiction: None.</p>","equipped":false,"price":0,"quantity":1,"volume":0.05,"weight":0.05,"addiction":5},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"2oqn6Iy7EPH48MYr":3},"flags":{},"_id":"8W9RR29uaoVsiN2i"}
