{"name":"Astral Reds","type":"pharmaceutical","img":"systems/vastgrimm/assets/images/icons/pharmaceuticals/capsules.png","data":{"description":"<p>Taken in pill form, +1 Presence per pill for 6 hours. However, this adjustment is stackable. Taking 2 incurs a 1 in 6 chance of a psychotic break, permanently reducing the user to a drooling idiot. Taking 3 is a 1-3 (d6) chance. Taking 4 is a 1-5 (d6) chance. Taking 5 or more causes an instant psychotic episode. Addiction: 1-2 (d20).</p>","equipped":false,"price":0,"quantity":1,"volume":0.05,"weight":0.05,"addiction":2},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"2oqn6Iy7EPH48MYr":3},"flags":{},"_id":"PpX5zsxwPJdpNQiT"}
{"name":"Rocket Stick","type":"pharmaceutical","img":"systems/vastgrimm/assets/images/icons/pharmaceuticals/molecule-1.png","data":{"description":"<p>Look Out! Rocket sticks are long flexible straws tipped with a soaked cotton end. They come 6 to a box. The user rubs these into their gums or other absorbent areas of the body. Increase Agility by 1. Acceleration of physical abilities allows for the character to always gain initiative. 1 in 10 sticks is a &ldquo;sick-stick&rdquo; and will cause the user to vomit uncontrollably for 2 rounds. Addiction: 1-5 (d20).</p>","equipped":false,"price":0,"quantity":1,"volume":0.05,"weight":0.05,"addiction":5},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"2oqn6Iy7EPH48MYr":3},"flags":{},"_id":"PvdDlNAWwXzHR1hF"}
{"name":"Stardust","type":"pharmaceutical","img":"systems/vastgrimm/assets/images/icons/pharmaceuticals/powder.png","data":{"description":"<p>Sparkling crystals in powder form, StarDust can be ingested, snorted, or smoked. StarDust brings a feeling of invulnerability and strength. Add +1 to Strength and Toughness. Subtract 1 from Presence. 2 in 6 chance a dose is a DustBust, causing -1 to all abilities. StarDust lasts for d6 hours. Addiction: 1-8 (d20).</p>","equipped":false,"price":0,"quantity":1,"volume":0.05,"weight":0.05,"addiction":8},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"2oqn6Iy7EPH48MYr":3},"flags":{},"_id":"jeg44fJUASvTgm5L"}
{"name":"Lotus Drop","type":"pharmaceutical","img":"systems/vastgrimm/assets/images/icons/pharmaceuticals/droplets.png","data":{"description":"<p>A golden liquid usually found in small dropper bottles, Lotus Drops bring euphoria and the ability to see a few seconds into the future. (For example, the characters arrive at a locked door. The character taking the lotus drop would have a vision of what would happen if they were to open the door. This glimpse into the future will only span 5-10 seconds after the proposed opening of the door.) Lotus drops do not give the ability to &ldquo;see through walls&rdquo; only to see and feel what &ldquo;might&rdquo; happen. After 2 uses of a Lotus Drop, the character must roll against addiction. Addiction brings the Lotus Sleep. The character refuses to move and instead only ingests the drops and stays in the dream state. Lotus Drops are highly addictive. Addiction 1-12 (d20).</p>","equipped":false,"price":0,"quantity":1,"volume":0.05,"weight":0.05,"addiction":5},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"2oqn6Iy7EPH48MYr":3},"flags":{},"_id":"k0IxsRx93YmCBQ31"}
